{"tid":1938341,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"高談大麻—毒品","createTime":"2020-03-22T13:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T22:36:10.000Z","uid":188644,"like":9,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"accfc6500eca132f6e7e9000f36ef1e1dc92913f","tid":1938341,"uid":188644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"果d話大麻唔係毒品既唔該搞清楚啦<br />\n首先 大麻喺當地係毒品 佢喺法律上就係毒品 係要坐監架 你話唔係毒品 咁你去警察面前隊番飛囉<br />\n第二 大麻喺定義上完全可以係毒品（當然都可以唔係） 有冇成癮性見人見智 咳藥水都可以係毒品 大麻點解唔可以係？<br />\n第三 過量吸食大麻係的而且確係對身體有副作用<br />\n第四 微辣既觀眾群唔係得你地架 仲有好多小朋友同青少年 佢地等陣真係信左你地既留言去食大麻比人拉左 係咪入你數先？<br />\n講到大麻好好咁 仲話人井底之蛙？話全世界好多地方都合法 係呀 好多地方都合法 但係有更多地方唔合法喎 <br />\n睇下個世界喎？真係搞笑 <br />\n全球得一個國家可以無限制購買大麻咋 即使加拿大最近大麻合法化都唔係可以任你買<br />\n誤導性留言仲以為自己好醒 世事都被你看透咁款<br />\n現實小小啦 佢喺你住既地方係毒品 佢就係毒品 除非你可以改變佢<br />\nP.S. 我其實都希望大麻合法化 但係希望大家唔好誤導人地 令人地因爲唔了解而犯法"},{"pid":"bdc45767b7c43bcb5450ce43a0dde2d84156ee94","tid":1938341,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"5b90bb052e7958f3a909f3b6090b01d99f94a706","tid":1938341,"uid":38772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51121be8be5d48f6ac021cfa4da082b7a3e2a057","tid":1938341,"uid":201495,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"一句到尾，禁煙好過禁大麻"},{"pid":"c618cf12fd3fd2f11ee2521e277d4916bc788c10","tid":1938341,"uid":5523,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"Tldr<br />\n總知大麻就係好野啦"},{"pid":"462561c64b0032a90f9f04c27caba8ab1ecc99d6","tid":1938341,"uid":108756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"我剩係覺得啲人信留言永遠係信個人問題<br />\n唔係留言個啲人既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細路/青少年 幫埋佢地屋企人教仔女好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他我都同意"},{"pid":"f484b3b68bc27f55d1a109948792c449890bb5ab","tid":1938341,"uid":177089,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"政府話大麻係毒品佢就係毒品<br />\n咁話黃絲係暴徒就係暴徒？"},{"pid":"ff9caa7febc6bcfd7a6bfb68b7616355cc3624c3","tid":1938341,"uid":326580,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"要禁大麻 就應該禁埋煙酒<br />\n既然開放煙酒 開放埋大麻亦未嘗不可"},{"pid":"0b57b81594548a4e21867ab0d1a02f44bbe109f4","tid":1938341,"uid":23468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0H3e5LW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0H3e5LW.jpg&h=b24d2f94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6Y3eEj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6Y3eEj.jpg&h=bf1c6fba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEDVQcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEDVQcG.jpg&h=d59cbb01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"201d185a23997ea45eba6c3ffa7da0ebecd134f8","tid":1938341,"uid":11506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"喺太空覆緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d496186b9380f5c25e376bfc15cd12b33d684b9","tid":1938341,"uid":349988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"要禁大麻 先禁煙<br />\n唔記得咗仲有啲支那電子煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cd0ca203055e84dd164f005b197a4f5fd52163","tid":1938341,"uid":71591,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法<br />\n爭取民主都唔可以破壞公物<br />\n唔理你理念幾高尚<br />\n現實少少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白痴"},{"pid":"709c3522fd8b42bddcf2bfb6d760027f3ab9e9a7","tid":1938341,"uid":123933,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"好耐無見大麻po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人仲記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw樓主你唔鍾意咪唔好食，我尊重你<br />\n但大麻真係唔係毒品呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 樓主思維：法例禁止=犯法=唔應該做<br />\n政府：港獨犯基本法，應該禁止港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個重點係套法律合時與否同合理與否嘛！<br />\n<br />\n2. 大麻成癮係心癮，過量飲可樂咖啡打牌賭波都有心癮，有害，你唔立法禁止人去做?<br />\n<br />\n3. 冇錯，長期過量吸食大麻係對身體唔好，所以政府更應加強立法規管同教育公衆，以保障市民安全，唔會食到啲黑心大麻，同有個正確harm reduction 嘅mind set！<br />\n<br />\n4. no comment 無睇微辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過網上係好多false and misleading information<br />\n希望樓主可以檢舉多啲唔同教壞細路嘅youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bca74ab26560766b8ec5f1bc489dff5dabda7c1","tid":1938341,"uid":48584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"樓主要寫文可以學下分段<br />\n唔係要令人睇得清晰 而係俾你自己望返清楚有冇邏輯謬誤"},{"pid":"a4579bfd54d5f750d04fe2fd685eda3813291be0","tid":1938341,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f484b3b68bc27f55d1a109948792c449890bb5ab","tid":1938341,"uid":177089,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"政府話大麻係毒品佢就係毒品<br />\n咁話黃絲係暴徒就係暴徒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"仲有佢第二點<br />\n笑撚死 咳藥水係毒品所以大麻都係<br />\n佢兩樣嘢毫無可比性<br />\n<br />\n咩邏輯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇睇微辣呢d垃圾片啊<br />\n見到你標題以為認真討論誰不知係度鳩up<br />\n衰過小學生辯論隊"},{"pid":"398cbf09be6508da9efdfc8b9e1ea43a67742445","tid":1938341,"uid":193843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"大麻內含成份有好多<br />\nTHC ,CBD 等<br />\n<br />\nCBD油真係好用 <br />\n舒眠、鎮痛、皮膚問題等<br />\n支持娛樂/醫療大麻合法化<br />\n大麻不是毒品 <br />\n<br />\n樓豬個標題寫得有夠差"},{"pid":"088c0ab172414a30eeda53384b9b36a5efec932d","tid":1938341,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"連登道友全面進場"},{"pid":"cdc35dd4710eea6bce7a8bc8c10a84389a772eb9","tid":1938341,"uid":218494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"User 留個名"},{"pid":"8ee2f6213f67b6c0c2db34c5d5e5b43af55e85f9","tid":1938341,"uid":88374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"同你講啦<br />\n其實班大麻友心態就係想學美國咁自由<br />\n但想學美國又唔識搞遊行<br />\n唔識公眾宣傳<br />\n淨係識圍威喂懶係勁咁<br />\n大麻合法化之後班友就冇得威<br />\n所以咪唔搞公開遊行囉<br />\n同埋唔敢搞遊行暗示班大麻友都知自己做既野唔見得光<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係大麻合法化左<br />\n7-11 circlek咪會同啲大麻舖爭生意囉<br />\n所以班大麻舖寧願圍內高價賣都唔想合化法<br />\n到頭來班咪又係講錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dc20f166e01aeab1eefa348ef8a0813a83b712","tid":1938341,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"中國唔合法 <br />\n但又出口大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c63a8b66c86e7d94703c03c8839cede0981408","tid":1938341,"uid":209786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"法律一定係啱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8879df9e215d2812457a07c7d27be69275fd6619","tid":1938341,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"成件事嘅關鍵根本唔係咩物質 或者合唔合法<br />\n而係有冇呢種文化嘅問題<br />\n歐美嘅大麻文化歷史久遠根深蒂固 即使係非法 啲人一樣會喺黑市買 所以先會合法化等政府有得規管下銷售渠道同產品宣傳<br />\n呢啲嘢你係冇興趣嘅就唔會掂<br />\n周街都有煙賣 你冇食開煙會唔會忽然去買?"},{"pid":"0385f63a87bf00da563cb52339dcf555268eb4e3","tid":1938341,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T23:38:13.000Z","msg":"樓主係連登屌大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525739b3f8ceefe41378fce5f51948ffb1875869","tid":1938341,"uid":53080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"一睇就知傻鳩藍絲廢中開po <br />\n<br />\n我諗你連咩係sativa indica都未知"},{"pid":"d484ba884a248919169330aa9f008f6a13361301","tid":1938341,"uid":279606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"大麻好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}